Package: openwatch
Version: 0.0.0
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: libc6 (>= 2.31), postgresql-client
Maintainer: OpenWatch Build <build@hanalyx.com>
Homepage: https://github.com/Hanalyx/openwatch
Description: OpenWatch Compliance Platform (Go binary)
 OpenWatch is the Go rebuild of the compliance scanning platform. This
 package ships the single binary, default TOML config, embedded demo
 TLS cert, and a hardened systemd unit. Operators replace the demo TLS
 material under /etc/openwatch/tls/ with their own certificate before
 production use.
